    <h2>How our virtual meetup works</h2>

    <p style="font-size:16px;font-style:italic">Our meetup is about learning the best ways to enable developers to find pair programming help. We'd love your input, please <a href="mailto:team@airpair.com" target="_blank">email us</a> your feedback & ideas.</p>

    <p>24 hours before each meetup, we'll send instructions in a meetup message with variations of the following steps.</p>

