    <p>Use the <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/pub?key=0AsOwlciMAOtXdDVEdFRJMUlyZFRlUHgzYnozOGhnTUE&output=html" target="_blank" style="color:#CC523E;font-weight:bold">google spreadsheet</a> to see who uses the same technologies & what everyone is interested in working on. Then start a conversation to see if it's a good fit.</p>

